divs: Sighting DetailsThis picture was taken by my buddy who is flying to New York as I speak , he was in terminal L10 Delta airlines at 2:45 PM and noticed this UFO shaped hole in the clouds ,as u can tell its huge and looks like a UFO ripped thru it, it caught his eye and a few other passengers in the terminal. I just thought I would post this in light of all the recent buzz over the UFO activity in the last months over O'Hare. My friend Tom who took the picture with his phone said that the clouds reformed and the hole was not visible by 3p.m so it was visible for 15 minutes

Summary: UFO shaped hole in clouds over O'Hare airport
